## FAQs

### Is it cheaper to rent or buy a sound system?

Renting versus buying a sound system often depends on your specific needs and frequency of use. Leasing can be more cost effective for occasional events or short term projects. However, purchasing might be a better investment if you require regular use. Consider factors such as maintenance, upgrades, and storage when deciding.

### How much does it cost to hire sound equipment?

The cost to hire sound equipment can vary based on the scale and type of event. At Malaga Event Gear, our pricing is competitive, with basic packages starting from:

– Small gathering: $200 – $300  
– Medium conference: $500 – $1,000  
– Large concert: $2,000 and above

Customization and add ons may affect the final pricing.

### How much does audio visual equipment cost?

The cost of audio visual equipment varies widely depending on the complexity and technology required. Malaga Event Gear offers exemplary solutions for diverse needs, from 290€+. You can find all the details on [our pricing page](https://malagaeventgear.com/pricing/).  
